  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add 2 slices of sourdough bread to the skillet and cook until golden and crispy on both sides.",
    "In a small bowl, mix 1/2 ripe avocado with 1 tablespoon lime juice, 1/4 teaspoon smoked paprika, 1/8 teaspoon red pepper flakes, and 1 tablespoon fresh cilantro.",
    "Top the crispy bread with the avocado mixture.",
    "Drizzle with 1 teaspoon olive oil for extra richness.",
    "Serve immediately while warm."
